'''Brusco Bouncer''' is a character in the [[Season 5|fifth]] season. He is played by [[Garry Mountaine]].<ref>[http://www.lbmactors.com/members/garry-mountaine/]</ref>
sections.In the books: In the ''[[A Song of Ice and Fire]]'' novels, there is a minor character by the name of Brusco, a Braavosi man who Arya meets, along with his whole family. However, Brusco does not employ bouncers in the books.
